<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir vormals <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den <expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan>
                        Molitor, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, und auch Hansen
                            <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener,
                        czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden gesant
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des czolls wegen, den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> von den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wider <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        brief und freiheit <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wil und
                                <expan>czeneme<ex>n</ex></expan> maint. Also
                            <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
                        aber darümb czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit die
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        burger und diener, und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>kunigl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>dymutikliche<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, daz sie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> küniglich gnade von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen darümb
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auszrichten wölle, als wir des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kunigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade wol
                        <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
